Each Assignor hereby assigns, transfers, and conveys to the Company all
right, title, and interest in and to the tangible business assets set
forth in the schedule below. Title to all such assets shall be held
exclusively by Provenarc Group LLC. Any personal property taxes,
insurance, or maintenance obligations with respect to such assets
accruing after the date of this Assignment shall be obligations of the
Company.

