**ARTICLE 3 --- CONSIDERATION**

In full and complete consideration for the assignments made herein, the
Company agrees to credit each Assignor\'s Capital Account with an amount
equal to the fair market value of the Assigned IP and Assigned Assets
contributed by such Assignor, as mutually agreed upon in a written
Capital Contribution Schedule to be appended to this Assignment within
thirty (30) days of execution. For IP Assets that have not yet been
commercially exploited and therefore lack a readily ascertainable market
value, the Members shall agree upon a conservative valuation or a
nominal valuation of One Dollar (\$1.00) per category of IP Asset until
a formal valuation is completed. No cash consideration is required
unless separately agreed in writing.

**ARTICLE 4 --- REPRESENTATIONS AND WARRANTIES**

Each Assignor, severally and with respect to their own contributions,
represents and warrants to the Company as follows:

-   The Assignor has full legal capacity, power, and authority to enter
    into this Assignment and to assign the Assigned IP and Assigned
    Assets as provided herein.

-   The Assignor is the sole and exclusive owner of all right, title,
    and interest in and to the Assigned IP and Assigned Assets being
    assigned by such Assignor, free and clear of all liens,
    encumbrances, licenses, claims, and third-party rights.

-   The Assignor has not previously assigned, transferred, or licensed
    any of the Assigned IP to any third party in a manner inconsistent
    with this Assignment.

-   The Assigned IP, to the best of Assignor\'s knowledge after
    reasonable inquiry, does not infringe upon, misappropriate, or
    otherwise violate the intellectual property rights of any third
    party.

-   There is no pending, threatened, or known basis for any claim,
    proceeding, or litigation involving the Assigned IP or Assigned
    Assets.

-   The Assignor has not received any written notice of any claim of
    infringement, misappropriation, or invalidity with respect to the
    Assigned IP.

